Midfielder Ake has been around the fringes of the first team this season and has started twice in the Capital One Cup and came on once in the Champions League.

Beeney, a goalkeeper, and midfielder Loftus-Cheek have not yet featured for the first team, although Loftus-Cheek has been captain of the youth team.

